UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PreCondition: The C2 field path has been cleared of Mines.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.Basic_Flow_of_Events: The troops traverse the field path.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PostCondition: The troops safely arrive at the field path destination.

UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PreCondition: C2 requires troop movement through a potentially mined field.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PostCondition: C2 has successfully moved troops to the field path destination within the mission duration time constraint.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.Basic_Flow_of_Events:
In order to rapidly clear a field path of Mines, C2 uses a UAV to perform a reconnaissance scan for each field cell.
Using AI, C2 analyzes the UAV scan stream and determines the probability of a Mines for each field cell.
Based on the results of the field scan, C2 determines a field path for UGV clearing that minimizes UGV neutralization time.
NOTE: The UGV takes time t1 to search and traverse a field cell with no found Mine. The UGV takes time t2 to search, neutralize and traverse a field cell with a found Mine (t2 > t1).
C2 deploys the UGV to clear the field path.
Upon completion of the UGV clearing, C2 instructs troops to traverse the field path.

UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PreCondition: C2 loads the UAV with coordinates of the environment "field cells" to be scanned for potential Mines.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PostCondition: The UAV returns to C2 and uploads high resolution result of the field scan.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.Basic_Flow_of_Events:
The UAV travels to the each field cell and scans the area using its on-board camera and sensors. The scan results are streamed back to C2 over the WAN.
NOTE: scan stream resolution is adapted based on WAN capacity.

UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PreCondition: A UGV is available from a near-by equipment depot.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.Basic_Flow_of_Events: C2 assigns a UGV from the depot to the mission and loads the field path to be cleared. The operator transports the UGV from the equipment depot to the field location.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PostCondition: The UGV is ready to begin field clearing.

UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PreCondition: C2 loads the field path (list of field cells) for the UGV to visit and clear of Mines. Each field cell includes a probability of Mine measure.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.Basic_Flow_of_Events: The UGV travels to each field cell, in the order prescribed by the field path, and neutralizes any found Mines.
UseCase_Description_Profile:requirementU.PostCondition: The UGV returns to C2 and uploads the results of the Mines neutralized along field path.
